<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="background">
		<div class="container" id="walkyHeader">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>WalkyTalky</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>
		
		<div class="container" id="signup">
			<div class="modal">
				<form method='post' id='signupForm'>
					<h3>Welcome to WalkyTalky!</h3>
					<p>Please provide this information:</p>
					<p><label>Create Username: <input type='text' name='username' id='usernameSignup'></label></p>
					<p><label>Select Password: <input type='password' name='password' id='passwordSignup'></label></p>
					<p><label>Confirm Password: <input type='password' name='confirm' id='confirmSignup'></label></p>
					<p><span class="error"></span></p>
					<button type='submit' name='signupButton'>Sign Up</button>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container" id="login">
			<div class="modal">
				<form method='post' id='loginForm'>
					<h3>Welcome to WalkyTalky!</h3>
					<p><label>Username: <input type='text' name='username' id='usernameLogin'></label></p>
					<p><label>Password: <input type='password' name='password' id='passwordLogin'></label></p>
					<p><span class="error"></span></p>
					<button type='submit' name='login'>Login</button>
					<p>New? <a href='#' id='signupLink'>Sign up</a> to create an account.</p>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div> 
		<div class="container" id="walkyTalky">
			<div id="walkyTalkyContainer">
				<div class="section" id="walkyMenu">
					<input type="button" id="addNewContact" class="button" value="Add New Contact">
					<input type="button" id="selectConversation" class="button" value="Select Conversation">
					<input type="button" id="deleteContact" class="button" value="Delete Contact">
					<input type="button" id="editMessage" class="button" value="Edit Last Message">
					<input type="button" id="deleteMessage" class="button" value="Delete Last Message">
					
				</div>
				<div id="conversation" class="section">
					<div id="welcomeMessage">
						<h3>Welcome to WalkyTalky <span id=welcomeUser></span>!</h3>
					</div>
					<div id="selectFriend">
						<form method='post' id='selectFriendForm'>
							<h3>Select a contact to start a message:</h3>
							<p>To start a message select your contact's name from the drop list below. You can only start conversations with people who are your contacts.</p>
							<p>If you do not see the person you are wanting to message make sure they are a WalkyTalky user, that you have added them as a contact, and that they have added you as a contact.</p>
							<p><label>Contact's Name:
								<select class="contactListSelect"></select></label></p>
							<p><span class="error"></span></p>
							<button type='submit' name='selectContact'>Select Conversation</button>
						</form>
					</div>
					<div id="addContactInfo">
						<form method='post' id='addFriendForm'>
							<h3>Enter your contact's username:</h3>
							<p>To add a new contact you need to know their WalkyTalky username. You cannot add contacts who do not have an account.</p>
							<p>You can add contacts who use WalkyTalky, but you will not be able to send them a message until they add you as a contact.</p>
							<p><label>Username: <input type='text' name='username' id='usernameAddFriend'></label></p>
							<p><span class="error"></span></p>
							<button type='submit' name='addContact'>Add Contact</button>
						</form>
					</div>
					<div id="messages">
						<form method='post' id='sendMessage'>
							<div id="messageList"></div>
							<input type='text' name='messageText' id='messageText'>
							<button type='submit' name='sendMessage' id='sendBtn'>Send</button>
						</form>
					</div>
					<div id="deleteFriend">
					<form method='post' id='deleteFriendForm'>
							<h3>Select a contact to remove:</h3>
							<p>To remove a contact you need to select them and confirm you want to remove the contact from your WalkyTalky connections.</p>
							<p>Removing a contact means the contact will no longer be able to send you messages. You will also not be able to send messages to them. It also means you will no longer be able to view your conversation with the contact.</p>
							<p><label>Contact's Name:
								<select class="contactListDelete"></select></label></p>
							<p><span class="error"></span></p>
							<button type='submit' name='deleteContact'>Delete Contact</button>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		</div>
		<script src="/scripts/clientLogin.js"></script>
		<script src="/scripts/contactManagement.js"></script>
		<script src="/scripts/chatManagement.js"></script>
		<script src=”/socket.io/socket.io.js”></script>
	</body>
</html>
